text: Aure is a municipality in Nordmøre in Møre og Romsdal county, Norway. In 2022, 3,384 people lived there. https://snl.no/Aure . SNL.no. Retrieved 2023-10-02 It has a wooden church called Aure Church. ==Related pages== *List of mayors in Norway that are elected until 2027 == References == Category:Municipalities of Møre og Romsdal
